				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Eh, the charm changes are a step but the nerf a-bomb of blasting all the old charm rules everywhere but wait you get a combo charm haste spell so when the new charms break your old pet is only 75% whirling death incarnate instead of 100% doesn't seem to balance out.  But MAYBE (big friggin maybe) with new WoM spells it may equal out but I didn't see anything in the brief description that was gonna make groups start wanting a charmed mob again versus safe old die to every aoe shiny bob (unless in their "review" of charmed dps they up it substantially). 
